name: Dark Fantasy
description:
Dark toned, dark skinned - but not always what you see. For once, we give rise to something that has i'm sure existed on CivitAI and other places for ages. We mean no harm, this is just our celebration, without nitpicking or anything - if we've done something incorrectly please let us know.

WE ARE PROUDLY SPONSORED BY: https://www.piratediffusion.com/

If you got requests, or concerns, We're still looking for beta testers: JOIN THE DISCORD AND DEMAND THINGS OF US: https://discord.gg/5t2kYxt7An
